## 🚦 How to use this

1. **Find your role** below (or use the [website](https://rahul-khare997.github.io/ai-toolkit-by-role/) to filter).
2. Start with **⭐ Must-have for everyone**, then your specific role.
3. Check the **Works in** column so you set it up in the right kind of tool.
4. Follow the **Docs** link for exact, up-to-date install steps.

> ⚠️ **Please read:** this is a community-curated starting point, not official docs. The AI space changes fast — always confirm install steps and permissions at the official **Docs** link before installing. Give connectors the *least* access they need (read-only when possible). Last checked: {{ generated_at }}.

